| Title validation | TC02: missing title → form error, no item saved |
| Description validation | TC03: missing description → form error, no item saved |
| Price validation — missing | TC04: empty price → form error, no item saved |
| Price validation — negative | TC05: negative price → form error, no item saved |
| Category validation | TC06: no category → form error, no item saved |
| Multiple missing fields | TC07: title + price empty → form error, no item saved |
| All fields empty | TC08: empty POST → form errors on all required fields, no item saved |

